<p>John and Dave are back after a well-deserved one-episode break with all your Mac goodness. &nbsp;Lots of Cool Stuff Found from both your favorite geeks and all of you listeners, plus we&#39;ve seen updates to Snow Leopard, iTunes, and even the iPhone deserves a mention. All that and more right here. Subscribe for free today and don&#39;t miss another episode!</p>
